ğŸ’¡ NOTES:
- Coupons can be single-use or multi-use (controlled via â€œMaximum Useâ€).  
- Coupons wonâ€™t work without an active and valid **Pricing Rule**.  
- ERPNext automatically prevents use after the expiry date or when the limit is reached.




