| Report Name                           | Description / Use                                                                 |
|----------------------------------     |----------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Sales Analytics                       | Analyze total sales by item, customer, territory, or time period. Helps measure sales performance and trends. |
| Sales Order Analysis                  | Detailed view of all Sales Orders with their status, items, and pending deliveries. Useful for tracking fulfillment. |
| Sales Funnel                          | Shows conversion flow â€” Lead â†’ Opportunity â†’ Quotation â†’ Order â†’ Invoice. Helps analyze conversion rates. |
| Sales Order Trends                    | Displays how Sales Orders vary over time (daily/monthly). Useful for demand forecasting. |
| Quotation Trends                      | Shows trends of sent, accepted, and lost quotations. Helps track quotation success rate. |
| Customer Acquisition and Loyalty      | Tracks new and returning customers. Helps understand loyalty and repeat purchase behavior. |
| Inactive Customers                    | Lists customers who havenâ€™t purchased for a long time. Helps target re-engagement campaigns. |
| Sales Person-wise Transaction Summary | Compares total sales achieved by each salesperson. Useful for performance evaluation. |
| Item-wise Sales History               | Shows product-wise sales quantity and amount over time. Helps identify best and worst-selling items. |


