| Report Name                                    | Description / Use                                                              |
|------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Customer Addresses and Contacts                | Displays all customer addresses and contacts in one place. Useful for data validation or CRM updates. |
| Available Stock for Packing Items              | Shows available stock for items that need to be packed or delivered. Helps in shipment readiness. |
| Pending SO Items for Purchase Request          | Lists Sales Order items that need to be purchased to fulfill delivery. Helps purchasing team plan. |
| Delivery Note Trends                           | Displays delivery patterns and frequency over time. Useful for logistics planning. |
| Sales Invoice Trends                           | Analyzes billing patterns and total invoices raised. Helps monitor revenue cycle. |
| Customer Credit Balance                        | Shows outstanding or advance balances per customer. Helps in credit control management. |
| Customers Without Any Sales Transactions       | Lists customers who have not made any purchase ever. Helps identify inactive or test accounts. |
| Sales Partners Commission                      | Displays total commission earned by sales partners based on their sales. Useful for partner accounting. |
| Territory Target Variance (Item Group-wise)    | Compares actual vs target sales in each territory per item group. Helps in territory performance tracking. |
| Sales Person Target Variance (Item Group-wise) | Shows difference between actual and target sales achieved by each salesperson. |
| Sales Partner Target Variance (Item Group-wise)| Compares target vs actual achievement for sales partners. Useful for commission-based reporting. |




























